{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#5385: Unnecessary move animation in nested <transition-group> ",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:26:40.585991+00:00",
  "text": "Unnecessary move animation in nested <transition-group> \n\n### Version\r\n3.2.30\r\n\r\n### Reproduction link\r\n[github.com](https://github.com/scx567888/error-example)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\nnpm run dev \r\nen :  and click green or red button to change sort\r\n中文 : 然后点击绿色或红色的按钮调整列表顺序\r\n\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\nen : Only the outermost div has transition animation\r\n中文 : 只有最外层的 div 有过渡动画\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\nen : Inner div also has transition animation\r\n中文 : 内部的 div 同样产生了过渡效果\r\n\r\n---\r\nen : i find add a css can fix this bug\r\n中文 : 我发现添加一个 css 可以修复这个 bug\r\n\r\n.scx-group-list-move .scx-group-list-move {\r\n    transition: unset;\r\n}\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->",
